```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Coordinator
    participant Agent01 as 01-Discovery
    participant Agent04 as 04-ETL
    participant Agent05 as 05-Heartbeat
    participant OnPremAPI as CyberArk On-Prem API
    participant PCloudAPI as Privilege Cloud API

    User->>Coordinator: python3 cli.py run P1
    Coordinator->>Agent01: run("P1")
    Agent01->>OnPremAPI: GET /Accounts
    OnPremAPI-->>Agent01: List of accounts
    Agent01->>OnPremAPI: GET /Safes
    OnPremAPI-->>Agent01: List of safes
    Agent01-->>Coordinator: result(status="success", data={...})
    Coordinator-->>User: Phase P1 complete

    User->>Coordinator: python3 cli.py run P4 (Pilot)
    Coordinator->>Agent04: run("P4")
    Agent04->>OnPremAPI: PATCH /Accounts/{id} (Freeze)
    OnPremAPI-->>Agent04: {status: "frozen"}
    Agent04->>OnPremAPI: POST /Accounts/{id}/Password/Retrieve
    OnPremAPI-->>Agent04: "password_value"
    Agent04->>PCloudAPI: POST /Safes (Create if not exists)
    PCloudAPI-->>Agent04: {safe_details}
    Agent04->>PCloudAPI: POST /Accounts (Import)
    PCloudAPI-->>Agent04: {account_details}
    Agent04->>OnPremAPI: PATCH /Accounts/{id} (Unfreeze)
    OnPremAPI-->>Agent04: {status: "unfrozen"}
    Agent04-->>Coordinator: result(status="success", data={...})

    Coordinator->>Agent05: run("P4")
    Agent05->>PCloudAPI: POST /Accounts/{id}/Verify
    PCloudAPI-->>Agent05: {verification_status}
    Agent05-->>Coordinator: result(status="success", data={...})
    Coordinator-->>User: Phase P4 complete
```